quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"Lɑ dũni-kãngã kɑ baa fʋɩ n zʋʋg kɩdeng la reem ye, lɑ ad Yɑoolem zɑkã, yẽ lɑ vɩɩm sẽn kɑ sɑɑbã tɩ b sã n dɑ yɩɩme n miẽ."
  29,65,"La b sã n wa zomb koom koglgo lɑ b sẽn n bõosd Wẽnde tɩ b yɑɑ sẽn n yɩlg b pʋs A kosgẽ wã; lɑ A sã n tɩlg-b n yiis yɩngã lɑ b sẽn mɑɑnd lɑgem-n-tɑɑr ne-A."
  29,66,"Bʋl yĩng tɩ b na kɩfl ne A sẽn n kõ bãmbã; b mɑɑn wʋm-noog tɩ bɩlf bɑlɑ b nɑ bãnge."
  29,67,"Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb ka yãnd tɩ Tõnd kõo bãmb Lohorem zĩig sẽn yaa bas-m-yam, tɩ b yaool n tabsda nebã bãmb tẽn-kɩrensã. Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb kɩta sɩd ne zɑɑlem la b kɩfend ne Wẽnd neemã wã?"
  29,68,"Lɑ ãnd n yɩɩd wẽgb ne ned ning sẽn wãagd-ɑ zĩri n dogl Wẽnd tɩ kɑ yɩ ne sɩda maa a yagsd sɩdã a sẽn wa n wa-a wã? Rẽ yĩnga, ka Gεhannem la kɩfr-rãmb gãag zĩigã?"
  29,69,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn nidg-b pãng Tõnd yĩngã, D nɑ kãndg-b D soyã zugu, lɑ bãng tɩ Wẽnd bee ne neb nins sẽn yɑɑ mɑnegdbã."
  30,1,"Alɩf, Lɑɑm, Miim."
  30,2,"B tõogɑ Rʋʋm-rãmba."
  30,3,"Tẽng sẽn pẽ yɑmbẽ ne bεεbã tẽngã (Fɑɑrɩs), lɑ b sẽn tõog-bã poorẽ b nɑ n tõogɑme."
  30,4,"Yʋʋm ɑ wãn poor bɑlɑ. Yellã tɑoor lɑ ɑ poor yɑɑ Wẽnd soolem, lɑ bɑrɑɑre sɩd-kõtbã nɑ n kɩdmɑme."
  30,5,"Ne Wẽnd sõngrã. A sõngdɑ A sẽn dɑt rãmbɑ, lɑ Yẽ lɑ ɑ Wilb lɑ ɑ Welg-n-yols Naaba."